Moren was starting to get bored talking to himself with no reason 
until he saw Pegatron starting to awake.
Moren:"Welcome back Peg."he said cheerfully.
Pegatron:"Umm....hun?Where`s Nightstrike?And Alpha?
Moren:"Don`t worry pal she`s safe and this crazy bot is gone 
somewhere.Wait a nano I`ll call the boss."he open a comm link"Yeah 
boss?Moren`s here,Peg is awake now."
Siref:"Good how is he doing?"
Moren:"Wait a moment."he turn to Pegatron"He wanna know how you`re 
feeling."
Pegatron:"Good still I wanna destroy that guy anyway."
Moren return to his call"He`s ok but still want his revenge."
Siref:"Good.Do what you want now.Over and out."

Pegatron was going out.Still his hand shaked a lot but wants no one 
to se it.And then he sit down.Dammit I`ve been here for not too long 
and there`s too many thing happening.Am I the problem or what?Anyway 
I`ve just got to relax now."
